These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, roller, van
1. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the van is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the airplane##2
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Transport   | skateboard | van | airplane | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, canasta, whist
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Game   | backgammon | snooker | whist | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dunhill, chaman, bolivar
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
2. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the chaman-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar   | old-henry | bolivar | chaman | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, davidoff, aristoff, alhambra
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
2. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the alhambra-smoker is between the pall-mall-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Cigar   | davidoff | pall-mall | alhambra | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
