2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Transport   | ship | boat | quad-bike | scooter |

