.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, dog, rabbit, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Pet   | rabbit | hedgehog | snake | dog |

 #################################

 
