.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, blues, jazz, hip-hop
1. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of blues and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | d&b | jazz | blues |

