.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, havana, aristoff, ritmeester
1. the havana-smoker is the havana-smoker##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | ritmeester | havana | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, polish, french, german
1. the french is in an odd position##4
2. the german is on the left of the french##1
3. the french is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | german | french | polish |

 